results.name: Square pyramid giving coefficients of Carlo Wood's polynomials, read by successive slices, each slice being read row by row.
comment: There is no standard method for converting a pyramid of numbers to a sequence. This seems as good a solution as any.
See the link for further information and more terms.
link: N. J. A. Sloane, Notes on Carlo Wood's Polynomials
